;。我覺得事故的最大原則就是救人，千方百計救人，只要有一線希望就要盡百倍努力。鐵道部門有關方面，是否做到這一點要給群眾一個實事求是的回答。<br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"a41e487a3c88c9e84d4fae61628e5d8d29ac82a9","tid":1766652,"uid":262488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T22:26:37.000Z","msg":"無死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3940a1fce40fa876f6a51d70dc6f810a081dc44c","tid":1766652,"uid":313974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a41e487a3c88c9e84d4fae61628e5d8d29ac82a9","tid":1766652,"uid":262488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T22:26:37.000Z","msg":"無死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T22:27:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfad62e66d6433b19a759666260f2ea60cd33d0f","tid":1766652,"uid":334806,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T22:32:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4mg8uMU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4mg8uMU.jpg&h=4203bda7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n支那：你地冇做錯到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69b06c663081390cd24243eeba0c13316f9689c4","tid":1766652,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T22:32:57.000Z","msg":"中国人思維：眼不見為乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"751ab993430491f93fc8243ca1830b915cdca301","tid":1766652,"uid":266026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T22:36:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HVENLmH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHVENLmH.jpg&h=711d1f3f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"de380ad3657a22f0d9bee681e75cf6cf4540a2be","tid":1766652,"uid":191139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T23:08:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"66230ca6cf2a7239dd5c9f74c35dc7a368acf28e","tid":1766